readable.content: A beige dog with a collar looks on as a brown dog swims in the water . A curly coated dog looking at another dog in the water . A curly haired dog is standing on a beach while staring at a dog in deep water . A white , curly haired dog is wearing a harness and watching another black and brown dog in the water . A wooly dog on a beach looks toward another dog in the water .
